OL,6,FHotel accommodation for British
OL,7,Ftourists in Catalonia has almost
OL,8,Freached "saturation point", according
OL,9,Fto a report from a respected Spanish
OL,10,Fresearch institute.
OL,12,FAfter a strong recovery following the
OL,13,Fpandemic, one of Spain's richest
OL,14,Fregions has reached the same or
OL,15,Fhigher number of visitors as in 2019,
OL,16,Fthe report by BBVA Research noted.
OL,17,FBut it warned that after Barcelona
OL,18,Fcouncil restricted hotel-building in
OL,19,Fthe city centre to combat
OL,20,Fovercrowding, accommodation for
OL,21,Ftourists will be limited.
OL,3,CBritish tourists face Spanish hotel
OL,4,Cshortage with Barcelona 'saturated'
